OL,3,C'Energy efficient supermarket fridges
OL,4,Care taking away my independence'
OL,6,FMs Williams said: "I live alone, I
OL,7,Fshop for myself and my 90-year-old
OL,8,Fmother who lives around the corner
OL,9,Ffrom me. I used to be able to do that
OL,10,Fcompletely independently, and now
OL,11,Fbecause of all these doors I simply
OL,12,Fcan't.
OL,14,F"Opening the doors and manoeuvring, I
OL,15,Fsimply don't have enough hands. You
OL,16,Fknow, I need one on my controls, and
OL,17,Fthen I'm opening the door with the
OL,18,Fother and then, you know, I've run out
OL,19,Fof arms."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
