OL,3,C'Energy efficient supermarket fridges
OL,4,Care taking away my independence'
OL,6,FShe continued: "I would really like it
OL,7,Fto go back to the way it was, because
OL,8,Fit's making me dependant on other
OL,9,Fpeople in a way that I don't want to
OL,10,Fbe, and in fact, don't need to be.
OL,12,F"People are quite literally running
OL,13,Fout of places where they can shop
OL,14,Findependently."
OL,16,FThe new chiller doors are being
OL,17,Finstalled to help supermarkets reach
OL,18,Fenergy efficiency targets, with one
OL,19,Fstore saying they save up to 40%.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
