OL,3,C'Energy efficient supermarket fridges
OL,4,Care taking away my independence'
OL,6,FBut campaigners have highlighted
OL,7,Fseveral problems connected with the
OL,8,Fdoors.
OL,10,FThey include wheelchair users not
OL,11,Fbeing able to reach some of the door
OL,12,Fhandles, the doors hitting
OL,13,Fwheelchairs, and the aisles becoming
OL,14,Ftoo narrow if two doors are open
OL,15,Fopposite each other.
OL,17,FThey have also brought up difficulties
OL,18,Ffaced by those who are visually
OL,19,Fimpaired, reporting reflections on the
OL,20,Fdoors can also make it hard for people
OL,21,Fto see through them.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
