OL,3,C'Energy efficient supermarket fridges
OL,4,Care taking away my independence'
OL,6,FGwen Johnson, from the charity
OL,7,FIndependent Specialist Support and
OL,8,FCare in Ashington, said: "A lot of
OL,9,Fpeople get a lot from going out into
OL,10,Fthe community, they need to be part of
OL,11,Fthe community, they need to be able to
OL,12,Fget into the shops.
OL,14,F"They need to be able to access their
OL,15,Fchoices when they're in there, and if
OL,16,Fshops are reducing that factor, it's
OL,17,Fabout freedom of choice, and that's
OL,18,Fnot really fair, it's not fair."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
