OL,6,FSainsbury's also said it is listening
OL,7,Fto customers as it tests the chillers.
OL,9,FWhile the Co-op said it is committed
OL,10,Fto balancing sustainability and
OL,11,Faccessibility and most of the chains
OL,12,Fhighlighted having staff to assist but
OL,13,FFlick says she and many others don't
OL,14,Fwant to have to rely on help.
